%}



ASCII_LETTER                            [a-zA-z]
// \p{Alphabetic} already includes [a-zA-z], hence we don't need to merge
// with {UNICODE_LETTER} (though jison has code to optimize if you *did*
// include the `[a-zA-Z]` anyway):
